                    <Copy
                      text={
                        "As the official host of Meet Magento Baltics, scandiweb brought the global Magento community to Riga. The event connected eCommerce professionals, merchants, and tech partners, offering them valuable insights into Magento, current eCommerce trends, and how to overcome real-world challenges. It was an impactful gathering, fostering learning and networking in the Baltic region and strengthening the local eCommerce ecosystem."
                      }
                      variant={"Inter/400/16/28/grey"}
                    />
